[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/43/16/431650.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1507567","time":"2019-10-10 19:24","userId":"fotile96","userName":"诚信肥肥","userSign":"(叶公好龙)","message":"对。。很多时候要拿notepad重新保存一下","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1507571","time":"2019-10-10 19:30","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"我选择删除foobar<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/31.gif\" smileid=\"70\" alt=\"(bgm54)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/18/171851.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1507574","time":"2019-10-10 19:33","userId":"yonjar","userName":"🍋LautlosP🍋","userSign":"(DD集まれ! (๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧)","message":"听说支持的是带BOM的utf8","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1507575","time":"2019-10-10 19:34","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"是啊..只支持带BOM的UTF8..不带BOM就出错.."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1508464","time":"2019-10-12 20:39","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 是啊..只支持带BOM的UTF8..不带BOM就出错..</q></div>？标准的UTF8不是没BOM的吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1508465","time":"2019-10-12 20:41","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow&#x1F319;</span> 说: ？标准的UTF8不是没BOM的吗</q></div>所以是不标准的UTF8?<br>反正Windows记事本保存UTF8文件时就会带BOM.."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1508476","time":"2019-10-12 20:58","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 所以是不标准的UTF8?<br>反正Windows记事本保存UTF8文件时就会带BOM..</q></div>因为UTF8没有字节序，所有字符一律从前往后读（也有*nix系统默认编码就是UTF8的关系）<br>微软酱的优先编码是本地编码（GBK/BIG5/JIS），然后是UTF16（这个有字节序），最后是UTF8，所以微软聪明的发明了BOM用来区分文件是16还是8……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1508486","time":"2019-10-12 21:18","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow&#x1F319;</span> 说: 因为UTF8没有字节序，所有字符一律从前往后读（也有*nix系统默认编码就是UTF8的关系）<br>微软酱的优先编码是本地编码（GBK/BIG5/JIS），然后是UTF16（这个有字节序），最后是UTF8，...</q></div>这么聪明为什么不选择猜编码<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1508713","time":"2019-10-13 08:19","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 这么聪明为什么不选择猜编码</q></div>因为猜编码靠统计，总有猜错的时候<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-7","id":"1508765","time":"2019-10-13 10:27","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow&#x1F319;</span> 说: 因为猜编码靠统计，总有猜错的时候</q></div>BOM也会出错就是了..<br>有不少程序根本不处理BOM..我选择标准的UTF8.."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#3-8","id":"1508771","time":"2019-10-13 10:40","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: BOM也会出错就是了..<br>有不少程序根本不处理BOM..我选择标准的UTF8..</q></div>不处理BOM的程序反而问题比较大吧…"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-9","id":"1508777","time":"2019-10-13 10:51","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: 不处理BOM的程序反而问题比较大吧…</q></div>我是<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/20167122\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">这个答案</a>提到的意思..shell之类的..<br>其实主要是有不可见字符让我很不自在.."}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1507590","time":"2019-10-10 19:52","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"(大破的那珂酱好萌！)","message":"这锅恐怕得甩给 Win32 API 吧（","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1507593","time":"2019-10-10 20:01","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"但不少Win程序都支持?"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1507594","time":"2019-10-10 20:08","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 但不少Win程序都支持?</q></div><div class=\"quote\"><q>因为Windows上并不存在什么UTF-8 No BOM的文件。记事本能打开其实是靠统计的，VS的话则是因为你们呼声太高了，学记事本统计。统计的意思就是这个功能是有问题的。Foobar的用户又对这个有什么需求？<br>——轮子哥</q></div>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#4-3","id":"1507595","time":"2019-10-10 20:16","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 但不少Win程序都支持?</q></div><div class=\"quote\"><q>Q: How I should deal with BOMs?<br><br>A: Here are some guidelines to follow:<br><br>1. A particular protocol (e.g. Microsoft conventions for .txt files) may require use of the BOM on certain Unicode data streams, such as files. When you need to conform to such a protocol, use a BOM.<br>2. Some protocols allow optional BOMs in the case of untagged text. In those cases,<br>       · Where a text data stream is known to be plain text, but of unknown encoding, BOM can be used as a signature. If there is no BOM, the encoding could be anything.<br>       · Where a text data stream is known to be plain Unicode text (but not which endian), then BOM can be used as a signature. If there is no BOM, the text should be interpreted as big-endian.<br>3. Some byte oriented protocols expect ASCII characters at the beginning of a file. If UTF-8 is used with these protocols, use of the BOM as encoding form signature should be avoided.<br>4. Where the precise type of the data stream is known (e.g. Unicode big-endian or Unicode little-endian), the BOM should not be used. In particular, whenever a data stream is declared to be UTF-16BE, UTF-16LE, UTF-32BE or UTF-32LE a BOM must not be used. (See also Q: What is the difference between UCS-2 and UTF-16?.) [AF]</q></div>如果有其他声明编码方式的办法，最好不要 BOM；反之建议都带 BOM。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#4-4","id":"1507597","time":"2019-10-10 20:19","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">板砖加身</span> 说: 因为Windows上并不存在什么UTF-8 No BOM的文件。记事本能打开其实是靠统计的，VS的话则是因为你们呼声太高了，学记事本统计。统计的意思就是这个功能是有问题的。Foobar的用户又对这个有...</q></div>来源是不是<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/60715689\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">这个</a>(b38<br>我不听 我不想要BOM 我选择猜编码<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> 编码如果一致就没有猜编码的问题了 嗯..<br>Foobar用户拿到的CUE也不保证都带BOM啊 不支持这个岂不是让一堆用户感到迷惑..而且记事本自己也懂猜编码呀.."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#4-5","id":"1507605","time":"2019-10-10 20:58","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 来源是不是这个(b38<br>我不听 我不想要BOM 我选择猜编码 编码如果一致就没有猜编码的问题了 嗯..<br>Foobar用户拿到的CUE也不保证都带BOM啊 不支持这个岂不是让一堆用户感到迷惑..而且记事...</q></div>你可以试试发动东亚用户去向波兰人施压，添加这个功能，我很乐意签个名 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#4-6","id":"1507607","time":"2019-10-10 21:02","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">板砖加身</span> 说: 你可以试试发动东亚用户去向波兰人施压，添加这个功能，我很乐意签个名 </q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"