像没问题?"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#11-3","id":"1508830","time":"2019-10-13 12:09","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: 试了下，打开ANSI （GB2312）编码的cue mpv直接关闭，我还是算了</q></div>看到一种说法，Linux 没有历史包袱，所以直接把所有文件当作 UTF-8 处理，因此就不存在猜编码这种事了 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#11-4","id":"1508835","time":"2019-10-13 12:23","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 我手动转码了一个 好像没问题?</q></div><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/9vzkyd.cue\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://files.catbox.moe/9vzkyd.cue</a><br><br>可以试试（音乐文件为うしろゆびさされ組 - バナナの涙.flac）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#11-5","id":"1508837","time":"2019-10-13 12:28","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: https://files.catbox.moe/9vzkyd.cue<br><br>可以试试（音乐文件为うしろゆびさされ組 - バナナの涙.flac）</q></div>我把CUE的文件名改成跟音乐文件同名 就可以了.. (Chapters全是乱码.."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#11-6","id":"1508865","time":"2019-10-13 13:32","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 我把CUE的文件名改成跟音乐文件同名 就可以了.. (Chapters全是乱码..</q></div>哦，应该是无法解码所以也无法获得里面引用的文件名<br><br>如果同名则可以外部判断的样子<br><br>不过其实MPV的UI怎么看chapters来着<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> 我用得少……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#11-7","id":"1508866","time":"2019-10-13 13:34","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: 哦，应该是无法解码所以也无法获